p.seg:
With these as witnesses: Simon, canon of Bethlehem; William, chaplain of
                  Tranent; Richard Ridel; Ralph of Graham; Payn of Hedley;
                  William of Graham; Simon of Thunderley; David of Lasswade;
                  Alured of Cranston; Alan and Stephen of Falside; Laurence and
                  Robert de Bonaire, and Bartholomew, burgesses of Edinburgh;
                  Gilbert the clerk; Michael Fleming; and many others.
